---
import arrow from "../../assets/icons/arrow-right.svg";
import heroImg from "../../assets/images/hero-img.jpg";
import checkIcon from "../../assets/icons/check-iconv2.svg";
---

<section
  id="sobre-mi"
  class="w-full bg-fondo flex justify-center items-center overflow-hidden py-16 lg:py-24"
>
  <div
    class="w-[90%] lg:w-[75%] max-w-[1440px] mx-auto flex flex-col lg:flex-row items-center gap-12"
  >
    {/* Left Content */}
    <div
      class="w-full lg:w-1/2 flex flex-col items-center lg:items-start text-center lg:text-left gap-5 lg:gap-8 lg:pr-10 pt-4 pb-8 lg:py-0"
    >
        <h1
          class="reveal text-4xl leading-[1.15] sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-[4rem] font-bold text-titulos px-4 sm:px-2 lg:px-0"
        >
          Recuperá tu <span class="text-primario">Movimiento</span>
          <br class="hidden sm:block lg:hidden" /> y Bienestar
        </h1>
      <p
        class="reveal delay-100 text-parrafos text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg px-6 sm:px-4 lg:px-0 max-w-md sm:max-w-lg lg:max-w-2xl mx-auto lg:mx-0 leading-relaxed"
      >
        Te acompañamos en cada paso de tu proceso con sesiones individuales y atención dedicada, en un espacio pensado <br> para que te sientas cómodo y cuidado
      </p>
      <div
        class="reveal delay-200 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 items-center w-full sm:w-auto mt-2 lg:mt-0 px-6 sm:px-0"
      >
        <a
          href="https://lnkinesiologia.site.agendapro.com/ar/sucursal/438392?fbclid=PAb21jcAQOyGRleHRuA2FlbQIxMQBzcnRjBmFwcF9pZA81NjcwNjczNDMzNTI0MjcAAadiWt7qF8JpBdmFJBK6rXJBuPjxiqVf372DtFCt3j8cshG8tdU0Xp91U0xHjQ_aem_6YX3DHUA-GxBmfvKHSOxEA&utm_content=link_in_bio&utm_medium=social&utm_source=ig"
          class="bg-titulos lg:bg-primario flex flex-row items-center justify-center rounded-xl lg:rounded-4xl px-8 py-4 gap-3 text-white text-base md:text-lg font-bold lg:font-medium hover:bg-primario lg:hover:bg-titulos transition-colors w-full sm:w-auto shadow-md"
        >
          <span>Pedir Turno</span>
          <img src={arrow.src} alt="Flecha" class="w-5 h-5 shrink-0" />
        </a>
        <a
          href="#servicios"
          class="bg-white border-2 border-titulos lg:border-[#E5E7EB] rounded-xl lg:rounded-4xl px-8 py-4 text-titulos lg:text-titulos text-base md:text-lg font-bold lg:font-medium transition-colors w-full sm:w-auto"
        >
          Ver Tratamientos
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    {/* Right Content — only visible on desktop */}
    <div
      class="reveal delay-300 hidden lg:flex w-full lg:w-1/2 relative justify-center items-center lg:pb-0 lg:mt-0"
    >
      <div
        class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[250px] h-[250px] md:w-[450px] md:h-[450px] bg-primario rounded-full -z-10 opacity-15 blur-[60px] pointer-events-none hidden lg:block"
      >
      </div>

      <div class="relative group w-full">
        <!-- Imagen principal -->
        <img
          src={heroImg.src}
          alt="Profesional kinesiologa realizando tratamiento"
          class="w-full max-h-[220px] sm:max-h-[260px] md:max-h-[300px] lg:max-h-none lg:w-[580px] object-cover rounded-2xl lg:rounded-[2.5rem] shadow-lg lg:shadow-2xl transform transition-transform duration-500 lg:rotate-2 group-hover:rotate-0 group-hover:scale-[1.02]"
        />

        <!-- Tarjeta superpuesta (Card) - solo desktop -->
        <div
          class="absolute -bottom-10 -left-12 bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl p-5 hidden lg:flex items-center gap-4 z-10 transition-transform duration-500 group-hover:-translate-y-2"
        >
          <div
            class="bg-[#E6F5F5] p-3 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center"
          >
            <img
              src={checkIcon.src}
              alt="Icono de Verificación"
              class="w-6 h-6"
            />
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col">
            <h3
              class="text-xs text-parrafos font-medium uppercase tracking-wider mb-1"
            >
              Pacientes Felices
            </h3>
            <p class="text-2xl font-bold text-titulos leading-none">+2000</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
